genresAdvancedInfo.name: irish black metal
genresAdvancedInfo.description: A sub-genre of heavy metal that combines the traditional sounds of Irish folk music with the aggressive and dark tones of black metal. This unique fusion creates a haunting and atmospheric sound that is both intense and captivating. The lyrics often draw on Irish mythology and history, adding an extra layer of depth and meaning to the music.
